# Uploads Directory

This directory contains user-uploaded files.

## Structure
- `profiles/` - User profile images
- `.gitkeep` - Ensures directory is tracked in git

## File Management
- Files are automatically organized by type
- Old files are cleaned up when users upload new profile images
- Maximum file size: 5MB
- Supported formats: JPEG, PNG, GIF, WebP

## Security
- All uploads are validated for file type and size
- Files are stored outside the web root for security
- Access is controlled through API endpoints
